Introduction

Keumjo is a South Korean singer and musical actress under Handa Productions. She is a former member of the girl group 9MUSES and its sub-unit 9MUSES A.

After the group's disbandment, she successfully debuted as a solo artist with her first Single Album "Fingertips" which was simultaneously released in Korean, Japanese, and Chinese on February, 12th 2020.

Fun facts

2
Keumjo is very famous in the industry for being a demo singer for songwriter e.one. She has done countless background or chorus vocals for groups like WJSN, April or KARA, to name a few, as well as solo artists and duos.
